The unified-fragmergent-memory-engine package composes three independent
source projects:
  - D_CORTEX_ULTIMATE
  - fragmergent-tf-engine
  - fragmergent-memory-engine
under namespaced passthrough wrappers. The unified package does not modify
the source projects. Each source carries its own license as documented in
its own repository.
